com.github.dm.jrt.util

Class WeakIdentityHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.util.WeakIdentityHashMap<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type.
    V - the value type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<K,V>

    public class WeakIdentityHashMap<K,V>
extends Object
implements Map<K,V>
    Map implementation combining the features of IdentityHashMap and WeakHashMap.

    Note that the map entries might change each time the object is explicitly accessed.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 11/17/2014.
